data.description: Stunning all brick home boasting curb appeal with lush landscaping and an inviting front porch! Walking in, you are greeted by a dining room with beautiful trim work and wainscoting, an office with french doors, and a spacious living room with a wood burning fireplace, vaulted ceilings, and access to the backyard. Off of the living room is the kitchen equipped with all stainless appliances, granite countertops, tile backsplash, a breakfast nook, and space for barstools. The home conveniently has a split bedroom plan with two secondary bedrooms and a full bathroom downstairs as well as the primary suite. The primary suite has a trey ceiling and en suite bathroom. The bathroom features a double vanity, separate shower, jetted tub, and walkin closet. Upstairs is the fourth bedroom with a full bathroom, walkin attic access, and a built in bookshelf. This home also features a large screened in back porch overlooking a beautiful lagoon and the 14th hole! Amenity packed neighborhood too!
